job.title: NJILOMD Technician Recruitment 2021  Apply Online  for 05 Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies:05

Name of the post:

  • Project Technician

Description:

The National JALMA Institute for Leprosy and Other Mycobacterial Diseases issued a total of 05 vacancies for the posts of Project Technician. The online application for these posts under NJILOMD shall start from 01.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 06.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for NJILOMD Technician Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Offline
  • No application fee
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 01.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 06.04.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the diploma/degree in 12th, Bachelor or Masters  to apply for the post of Project Technician

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 21 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 30 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Project Technician is INR 18000-31000/month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed Vacancies:

  • Project Technician III
  • Project Assistant

How to apply for NJILOMD Technician Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of NJILOMD.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of the Project Technician.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
